  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Data of patient reported outcomes (PRO) are collected during treatment with various pain
      alleviation methods (drugs or substances)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study aims at collecting BPI (brief pain inventory) and other PRO of patients in need of
      pain relief due to chronic orthopedic pain conditions
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
